constructor.notice: An epic battle to the death for a last man standing to win an NFT of their fighter and some SNX.

endGame().notice: End the game (if we haven't already.)  Can be called from public to reset the game.

getMyTokens().notice: Get my tokens helper function for front-end usability. Concept borrowed from CryptoKitties.

joinGame().notice: Join the game by requesting a new random number to generate my fighter.

rewardPlayer(address,(uint256,uint256,ui.notice: Mint the NFT for the winning player. Transfer some SNX to them as well (I think).
